{"tid":1350444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[光復香港］越嬲越要做好文宣","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:01:35.000Z","uid":78068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3b22351e159d1464f6b36bca2d73a094b63ef2","tid":1350444,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"好嬲 嬲自己見住黑官警勾結而無嘢做到嘅<br />\n中上環一帶嘅開三十幾槍 無人關注 好嬲<br />\n越嬲 越要去連儂牆發洩下<br />\n有好多嘢我哋都睇過 成個同溫層都睇過<br />\n但啲街坊無 我哋咁多證據喺手 道理根本喺我哋嗰邊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>做社區教育有無用？</strong></span></span><br />\n我唔直接答你 用相答你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6q87KNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6q87KNQ.png&h=e6a7df3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsTLwsR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsTLwsR.png&h=bff16fda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7fb7884f57d0b0c7517d40a9cb8325237121e57","tid":1350444,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c1bce3e1ba0bf407b57e308e826a6a5f5b0d4ba","tid":1350444,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ece20db2629cb32fafdbb6e97e55cbd873b2785a","tid":1350444,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9aaed587e7f2d0a39e2348bd3b83970012fc3734","tid":1350444,"uid":286285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdbk41L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmdbk41L.png&h=4cb231e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a90f2349715b07ea30b63b78391f3f2e35f2c510","tid":1350444,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}